<package format="1" xmlns="https://wiki.freecad.org/Package_Metadata">
  <name>PushPull</name>
  <description>SketchUp-style direct modeling for FreeCAD: click a planar face on a PartDesign Body, drag along its normal with a live ghost preview and numeric readout, release (or type a distance and press Enter) to commit a real parametric PartDesign Pad (outward) or Pocket (inward). No live OCCT recompute during the drag -- only a cheap Coin3D ghost is updated per mouse tick.</description>
